# No Cursor attribution

Never add any of the following to commit messages, PR descriptions, or code:

- `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>`
- `Made-with: Cursor`
- Any other Cursor co-author or attribution trailer

The repository strips these automatically in `prepare-commit-msg`; do not add them.
